test_name: DSCOGST compared to Form D1a NORMCOG
short_desc: If NORMCOG = 1, then DSCOGST should equal 1
full_desc: If Form D1a, Q2. NORMCOG (participant have unimpaired cognition & behavior) = 1 (yes), then Q6. DSCOGST (What is the participant’s cognitive status?) should equal 1 (cognitively stable)

test_name: DSCOGST compared to Form D1a MCI
short_desc: If MCI = 1, then DSCOGST should equal 2
full_desc: If Form D1a, Q4b. MCI (participant meets criteria for MCI) = 1 (yes), then Q6. DSCOGST (What is the participant’s cognitive status?) should equal 2 (MCI - DS)

test_name: DSCOGST compared to Form D1a DEMENTED
short_desc: If DEMENTED = 1, then DSCOGST should equal 3
full_desc: If Form D1a, Q3. DEMENTED (participant meet criteria for dementia) = 1 (yes), then Q6. DSCOGST (What is the participant’s cognitive status?) should equal 3 (Dementia)

test_name: DSCOGST aligns with the previous visit
short_desc: If DSCOGST[prev_vis]=3 then DSCOGST should not equal 1
full_desc: If Q3. DSCOGST (Whatis the participant's cognitive status) = 3 (Dementia) from previous visit, then Q3. DSCOGST (Whatis the participant's cognitive status) should not equal 1 (Cognitively stable)

test_name: Valid value of DSHEADCM provided at previous visit
short_desc: If DSHEADCM = 777, DSHEADCM[prev_vis] should be between 45 and 70 or 777
full_desc: If Q1. DSHEADCM (Head circumference (cm)) = 777, Q1. DSHEADCM[prev_vis] should be between 45 and 70 or =777
test_logic: If DSHEADCM=777 and DSHEADCM[prev_vis] not between 45 and 70 or =777

test_name: Valid value of DSCHROM provided at previous visit
short_desc: If DSCHROM = 7, DSCHROM[prev_vis] should be between 1 and 3 or 7
full_desc: If Q5. DSCHROM (participant's chromosome diagnosis) = 7, Q5. DSCHROM[prev_vis] should be between 1 and 3 or =7
test_logic: If DSCHROM=7 and DSCHROM[prev_vis] not between 1 and 3 or =7
